4, United States</aff><author-notes><fn fn-type="other" id="FN1"><label>f</label><p id="P1">Co-authorship</p></fn><fn fn-type="con" id="FN2"><p id="P2">Author information</p><p id="P3">J.D.S. conceived of and designed this project, generated data for <xref rid="F2" ref-type="fig">Figure 2</xref>, wrote a portion of the manuscript draft, and edited the manuscript. K.M.N. generated data for <xref rid="F3" ref-type="fig">Figure 3</xref>, <xref rid="T2" ref-type="table">Table 2</xref>, and <xref rid="SD1" ref-type="supplementary-material">Figures S1</xref>&#8211;<xref rid="SD1" ref-type="supplementary-material">S11</xref>, performed data analysis for <xref rid="F4" ref-type="fig">Figure 4</xref>, wrote a portion of the manuscript draft, and edited the manuscript. J.R.G. generated data for <xref rid="SD1" ref-type="supplementary-material">Figures S12</xref>&#8211;<xref rid="SD1" ref-type="supplementary-material">S13</xref>, wrote a portion of the manuscript draft, and performed data analysis for <xref rid="F4" ref-type="fig">Figure 4</xref> and <xref rid="SD1" ref-type="supplementary-material">Table S1</xref>. S.D. assisted with data generation for <xref rid="F3" ref-type="fig">Figure 3</xref> and <xref rid="T2" ref-type="table">Table 2</xref>. E.E.C. contributed to project design, data analysis, and manuscript editing.</p></fn><corresp id="CR1"><label>*</label>Corresponding Author (<email>carlsone@umn.edu</email>)</corresp><fn fn-type="COI-statement" id="FN3"><p id="P30">The authors declare no competing financial interest.</p></fn></author-notes><pub-date pub-type="ppub"><day>13</day><month>12</month><year>2024</year></pub-date><pub-date pub-type="epub"><day>04</day><month>12</month><year>2024</year></pub-date><volume>10</volume><issue>12</issue><issue-id pub-id-type="pmc-issue-id">486345</issue-id><fpage>4137</fpage><lpage>4145</lpage><pub-history><event event-type="nihms-submitted"><date><day>04</day><month>04</month><year>2025</year></date></event><event event-type="